{"tid":2257113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港電台：台中市有住宅起火　一死兩傷","createTime":"2020-10-25T02:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T02:17:43.000Z","uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0395d1f9195660f8768602fd23daf9b340269939","tid":2257113,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556540-20201025.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556540-20201025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=109d2e51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556540-20201025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a806e7e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556540-20201025.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n台中市有住宅發生火警，一死兩傷，當局調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n消防昨晚11時許接報，指大雅區有住宅起火。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場後，在後門發現一名年約50多歲的男子及他80多歲的母親，將兩人送院。男子說，妹妹被困屋內。<br />\n<br />\n消防之後在一樓的房間找到一名女子，送院後不治。<br />\n<br />\n鄰居表示，屋主的妹妹長期臥床。"}]}